        "creatureType": "",
        "details": {
            "description": "<p>A portal to the Plane of Air rips open onstage, causing roaring winds to tear through the opera house</p>",
            "disable": "<p><span data-pf2-check=\"arcana\" data-pf2-traits=\"hazard,environmental,magical,air\" data-pf2-label=\"Air Rift Arcana DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"38\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Arcana</span> (master) to sew the magical threads of the rift shut, <span data-pf2-check=\"nature\" data-pf2-traits=\"hazard,environmental,magical,air\" data-pf2-label=\"Air Rift Nature DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"40\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Nature</span> or <span data-pf2-check=\"survival\" data-pf2-traits=\"hazard,environmental,magical,air\" data-pf2-label=\"Air Rift Survival DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"40\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Survival</span> (legendary) to open enough windows and doors to reduce its intensity, or @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Dispel Magic]{Dispel Magic} (7th level; counteract DC 34) to counteract the air rift</p>",
            "isComplex": true,
            "level": {
                "value": 14
            },
            "reset": "",
            "routine": "<p>(1 action) Winds blow through the area in a random direction, causing creatures and objects within 50 feet of the air rift to float up, down, north, south, east, or west (roll a d6 to determine which direction). Creatures and objects in the area must attempt a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect,air, environmental,magical,hazard\" data-pf2-label=\"Air Rift DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"37\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save. If a creature is pushed into a solid object or another creature by this effect, both take [[/r 3d8+15 # bludgeoning damage]]{3d8+15 bludgeoning damage} on impact.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is pushed 10 feet, but takes only half damage from impact.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is pushed 20 feet, falls prone, and takes full damage from impact.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is pushed 40 feet, falls prone, and takes double damage from impact.</p>"
        },
